whomap 0.7.10
----------------------------------------------------------------

* fixes to pass devtools::check()

* additional unit tests


whomap 0.8.0
----------------------------------------------------------------

NEW FEATURES

* `add_marker()` plots secondary country markers (R shapes).

* Add an internal dataframe centroid, which holds the coordinates
of country centroids.



BUG FIXES AND MINOR IMPROVEMENTS

* whomap returns a ggplot2 object instead of printing it.

* Default legend position updated.
